column1: # List of PubMed IDs of all publications whose CLIP & CLASH data sets have been integrated in StarBase 2.0.
# Created by Alexander Junge on Sep 9, 2014 the following semi-automatic way (in lack of a fully automatic solution):
# Download html source of http://starbase.sysu.edu.cn/download.php after opting to show 'All' entries. Save website source as StarBase.html.
# Then the following command yields the list below:
# cat StarBase.html | perl -ne '/http:\/\/www\.ncbi\.nlm\.nih\.gov\/pubmed\/(\d+)/ && print $1 . "\n"' | sort | uniq > starBase_2.0_Experiments_PubMedIDs.tsv
